articles.title: OnePlus Pad Go will go on sale in Europe from April 23 - 9to5Google
articles.description: OnePlus has confirmed that the OnePlus Pad Go – a mid-range Android tablet – is set to go on sale in Europe from April 23.
articles.content:
OnePlus has confirmed that the OnePlus Pad Go a mid-range Android tablet is set to go on sale in Europe from April 23.
